data.description: PRICE ADJUSTMENT!!! DOWN PAYMENT ASSISTANCE IS AVAILABLE. CALL TO INQUIRE. Welcome to this delightful single-story, perfectly situated across the street from a picturesque park, offering a seamless blend of modern living and outdoor enjoyment. The Westmont area of Pomona is Diamond Bar and Phillips Ranch adjacent. This well-loved home features: Three bedrooms, two beautifully renovated bathrooms, ensuring comfort and convenience. An open-concept design that creates an inviting and airy atmosphere, with the living room, dining room, and kitchen seamlessly connected. The kitchen is perfect for hosting and entertaining. The primary bedroom suite is a sanctuary of its own, featuring a private bathroom. The backyard is a blank canvas, ready for your personalized design and landscaping dreams. It's an ideal space for creating your own oasis, hosting barbecues, or simply enjoying the serene California weather. The park just across the street is like an extension of your own backyard. Stroll across to enjoy the greenery or take a leisurely walk, it's right at your doorstep. This home is conveniently located within shopping, schools, and dining options just a short drive away. Commuters will appreciate the easy access to major roadways. This property offers the quintessential California lifestyle, where indoor and outdoor living blend seamlessly. Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your home. Contact us today to schedule a showing and discover the countless possibilities that await you at this amazing residence.
